      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Harlem%2C_Florida"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "In 1926 a Black settlement on Lake Okeechobee was moved to what is now Harlem, marking its earliest roots.",
